        "authorId" : "a08d3bc9-3f30-4d94-a529-7f2d27085022",
        "body" : "Look through and seems we can remove `hdf5` and `openblas` which have run exports. I've also added `cudatoolkit` and `armadillo` to ignore their run exports, as the former is linked statically, and the latter just uses the includes when building and not the library when running",
