        "authorId" : "a08d3bc9-3f30-4d94-a529-7f2d27085022",
        "body" : "At the moment the linker line uses `-lopenblas` explicitly. Would it be better to make `openblas` only with:\r\n```\r\nrequirements:\r\n  host:\r\n    - openblas\r\n  run:\r\n    - libblas * *openblas\r\n    - openblas\r\n```\r\nor to change the linker line to `-lblas` and have:\r\n```\r\nrequirements:\r\n  host:\r\n    - libblas\r\n```",
        "createdAt" : "2020-04-16T10:42:21Z",
        "updatedAt" : "2020-04-16T10:57:32Z",
        "lastEditedBy" : "a08d3bc9-3f30-4d94-a529-7f2d27085022",
